top_stories.title: Intuit and OpenAI join forces on new AI-powered experiences

top_stories.title: AI mania is making Nvidia a lot of money
top_stories.description: AI companies are spending so much on infrastructure that Nvidia’s data center business now brings in nearly $50 billion.
